        96.0,
        69.65,
        357.04,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p044_s0006",
      "text": "The format of the LS_ACC Payload is shown in table 6.  The Payload shall contain the revised end-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        94.97,
        540.07,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p044_s0007",
      "text": "to-end Credit allocated in the Credit field for the appropriate Class Service Parameters as indicated",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        539.88,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p044_s0008",
      "text": "by the Class Validity bit.  The revised end-to-end Credit shall replace the end-to-end Credit for the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        539.93,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p044_s0009",
      "text": "current Login for the Nx_Port transmitting the LS_ACC Sequence (see 6).  For each class in which a",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        540.13,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p044_s0010",
      "text": "revised end-to-end Credit is updated, the Class Validity bit shall be set to one.  The recipient shall ig-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.96,
        539.9,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p044_s0011",
      "text": "nore the other Service Parameter fields. This revised end to-end Credit value is determined by the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.96,
        540.01,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
